  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2e3b85ba0ef1eac4682a23cb38907d1b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Necromancer_1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Dialogues
  npcName: Necromancer(HURT)
  npcSprite: {fileID: 2386087392262683051, guid: 22b5220aaa001f74aa6ed0d66f7a9028, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - "Stop. Don't waste your breath asking for the way out. There is no path left
    in these woods. I\u2019ve looked for eighty years... my legs gave out before
    the forest did."
  - "Kill me if you like, but it won't open the fog. There is a sunken tomb nearby\u2014a
    dungeon of bone and filth."
  - I found the key once, but the skeletons there... they broke my spirit. And my
    body.
  - Listen. There are relics in that dark hole. Ancient anchors that hold this forest
    in a loop. If you have the steel to clear that place, bring the items to me.
  - I still remember the old rites to break the seal. You be the sword, and I'll
    be the voice.
  - It's the only way we aren't buried here.
  - But I know you won't trust me so take this with you..
  - This potion will heal you as long as you use it wisely! Best Of Luck...
  - ....Obtained Magical Potion....
  typingSpeed: 0.05
